# 🔹 GROUP 7 — Determinism (critical)

---

## 19. Transformation preserves determinism ⭐

### T

Apply transformation (rename, reorder, etc.)

### R

Still deterministic

```python
f(x) == f(x)
f(T(x)) == f(T(x))
```

